                <h1>HRL reinstates two of three Resident Assistants it fired related to tenting</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/6b4ea9d9-3430-4d73-a5da-200fb7bd9dff.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            

